  "detailed_description": "<strong>Mine gems, collect pickaxes, battle bosses, and explore treasure-filled biomes!</strong><br><br>Elevate your idle gaming experience with PickCrafter, now available on desktop! Smash blocks and reap the rewards in this captivating pixel-style clicker. Forge Legendary Pickaxes and gear to dominate the world of Runaria. <br><br>Prestige through Extravagant, Transcendent, Preposterous, and Legendary tiers. Craft intricate strategies with the new Ascension Skill Tree, and etch your name into the annals of legends!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/734750/extras/a9ed9549aea1065a779015e2db1a97a6.avif?t=1772474111\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><br>Set forth on a journey to discover all the Biomes, from the snow-clad Tundra to the alien landscapes of the Moon and Mars. Unearth their mysteries and uncover hidden treasures!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/734750/extras/7bf97a98fae0f21fc68ef5e277ab1f61.avif?t=1772474111\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br>Unleash your inner strength with unlockable Abilities. Forge powerful equipment and supercharge your furnaces. Craft, upgrade, and dominate in PickCrafter!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/734750/extras/bbf2610117315ddd37bca0b6928af31e.avif?t=1772474111\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br>Challenge your friends, climb the leaderboards, and complete over 120 remarkable achievements. Rare, Epic, and Legendary items await you!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/734750/extras/01507265b45439fe32cfd656af4e0102.avif?t=1772474111\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br>Download now and become the ultimate treasure hunter in this endlessly addictive adventure. Your fortune awaits!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/734750/extras/86fecb80aafaa301f5da0d5fbbfa65a0.avif?t=1772474111\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br>Join our Community Discord Server to suggest exciting new features and share your invaluable feedback!",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Mine gems, collect pickaxes, battle bosses, and explore treasure-filled biomes!</strong><br><br>Elevate your idle gaming experience with PickCrafter, now available on desktop! Smash blocks and reap the rewards in this captivating pixel-style clicker. Forge Legendary Pickaxes and gear to dominate the world of Runaria. <br><br>Prestige through Extravagant, Transcendent, Preposterous, and Legendary tiers. Craft intricate strategies with the new Ascension Skill Tree, and etch your name into the annals of legends!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/734750/extras/a9ed9549aea1065a779015e2db1a97a6.avif?t=1772474111\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><br>Set forth on a journey to discover all the Biomes, from the snow-clad Tundra to the alien landscapes of the Moon and Mars. Unearth their mysteries and uncover hidden treasures!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/734750/extras/7bf97a98fae0f21fc68ef5e277ab1f61.avif?t=1772474111\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br>Unleash your inner strength with unlockable Abilities. Forge powerful equipment and supercharge your furnaces. Craft, upgrade, and dominate in PickCrafter!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/734750/extras/bbf2610117315ddd37bca0b6928af31e.avif?t=1772474111\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br>Challenge your friends, climb the leaderboards, and complete over 120 remarkable achievements. Rare, Epic, and Legendary items await you!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/734750/extras/01507265b45439fe32cfd656af4e0102.avif?t=1772474111\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br>Download now and become the ultimate treasure hunter in this endlessly addictive adventure. Your fortune awaits!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/734750/extras/86fecb80aafaa301f5da0d5fbbfa65a0.avif?t=1772474111\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br>Join our Community Discord Server to suggest exciting new features and share your invaluable feedback!",
